Despite that, I'm happy with the website. The video quality is good and easy to follow along to, and it's lovely having so much great music to choose from. Now for the hard part - playing it!

## Takeaway Points

- Progress bars remain the most interminably difficult part of workflow engine development.
- It is known that setting up a cluster-computer render farm is a prerequisite to playing piano.
- Playing piano is still difficult.
